import math

def calculate_expected_value_floor(T, test_cases):
    results = []
    for i in range(T):
        (N, A_array) = test_cases[i]
        results.append(math.floor(sum(A_array) * N))

import math

def calculate_expected_value_floor(T, test_cases):
    results = []
    for i in range(T):
        (N, A_array) = test_cases[i]
        results.append(math.floor(sum(A_array) // N))
    return results
